data.text:
Andrew Roberts, 83, of Point, passed away Monday, Sept. 23, 2013 at his home. He was born January 9, 1930 in Pittsburgh, PA to Thomas and Ann Patronie Roberts, Sr. He married Frankie Deloris Jones in Rains County on April 30, 1962. He retired from the United States Air Force, with rank of

Master Sergeant, after 20 plus years of service.

Survivors include:

Daughters: Sandra Armstrong and husband John of Omaha, NE;

Karen Duvall and husband Tom of Cannonsburg, PA;

Jan Roberts of Point, TX;

Ann Rodriguez and husband George of Point, TX;

Sons: Donald Gene Roberts and wife Cindy of Point, TX;

Drew Roberts and wife Susan of Point, TX;

Brothers: 4;

Grandchildren: Scott, Courtney, Tamara, Thomas Jr., Nina, Dustyn, Zachary, Sandra, Micah, Jennifer, Andrew, Tiffani, Charles, and Fran;

Great-Grandchildren: 17;

Numerous other loving family and friends.

Preceded by:

Parents; Wife, January 2003; and 1 Granddaughter.

In Lieu of flowers please donate to charities of your choice.

Memorial service is scheduled for Saturday 10:00 AM, October 5, 2013 at 5232 CR 3521 Quinlan, TX 75474.

Cremation arrangements are under the direction of

Wilson-Orwosky Funeral Home.
